Third-Party Components and Dependencies
========================================

This project uses the following third-party libraries:

Core Dependencies (from conanfile.py)
--------------------------------------

1. OGDF (Open Graph Drawing Framework) - v2023.09
   License: GPL-2.0-or-later / GPL-3.0-or-later
   Website: https://ogdf.uos.de/
   Note: This is the primary reason this project must be GPL-licensed.

2. Eigen Linear Algebra Library - v3.4.x
   License: Mozilla Public License 2.0 (MPL-2.0)
   Website: https://eigen.tuxfamily.org/
   Note: Configured with MPL2_only=True to use only MPL-2.0 licensed portions.

3. spdlog - v1.15.x
   License: MIT
   Website: https://github.com/gabime/spdlog

4. stduuid - v1.2.x
   License: MIT
   Website: https://github.com/mariusbancila/stduuid

5. argparse - v3.2
   License: MIT
   Website: https://github.com/p-ranav/argparse

6. nlohmann_json - v3.11.3
   License: MIT
   Website: https://github.com/nlohmann/json

7. autodiff - v1.1.2 (via CMake FetchContent)
   License: MIT
   Copyright: Allan Leal (2018-2024)
   Website: https://github.com/autodiff/autodiff

8. nanobind (Python bindings)
   License: BSD-3-Clause
   Website: https://github.com/wjakob/nanobind


Transitive Dependencies
------------------------

The following libraries are transitive dependencies (dependencies of dependencies):

1. COIN-OR Libraries (CoinUtils, Clp, Osi)
   License: Eclipse Public License 2.0 (EPL-2.0)
   Website: https://www.coin-or.org/
   Note: Used by OGDF

2. pugixml
   License: MIT
   Website: https://pugixml.org/

3. zlib
   License: Zlib License
   Website: https://www.zlib.net/

4. bzip2
   License: bzip2-1.0.6
   Website: https://sourceware.org/bzip2/


