License Summary
===============

Due to the dependency on OGDF (GPL-2.0-or-later/GPL-3.0-or-later), this entire
project is licensed under GPL-3.0-or-later.

The majority of other dependencies use permissive licenses (MIT, BSD, Apache, etc.)
which are compatible with the GPL.

Eigen uses MPL-2.0, which is a weak copyleft license and is also compatible with GPL.

COIN-OR uses EPL-2.0, which is compatible with GPL as per the Eclipse Foundation's
compatibility statement.


